OL,3,CWorking age households predicted to be
OL,4,C#400 worse off on average in year ahead
OL,6,FWorking age households are on track to
OL,7,Fbe #400 worse off on average in the
OL,8,Fyear ahead amid income squeezes and
OL,9,Fbill hikes, a think-tank predicts.
OL,11,FAs the new tax year gets under way in
OL,12,FApril, households face a "triple hit"
OL,13,Ffrom the impacts of tax, utility bill
OL,14,Fincreases, and benefits that are not
OL,15,Fkeeping pace with the cost of living,
OL,16,Fthe Resolution Foundation said.
