OL,6,FLong-running freezes to personal tax
OL,7,Fthresholds will mean some people are
OL,8,Fdragged into paying more tax, while
OL,9,Femployer national insurance (NI) hikes
OL,10,Fwill feed through to households
OL,11,Fthrough slower wage growth as
OL,12,Femployers recoup costs, the Foundation
OL,13,Fpredicts.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, rising utility bills and
OL,16,Fcouncil tax will put further pressure
OL,17,Fon household budgets, the report said.
