OL,6,FChanges from April mean the national
OL,7,Fliving wage for those aged 21 and over
OL,8,Frises from #11.44 per hour to #12.21
OL,9,Fper hour.
OL,11,FThe national minimum wage for 18 to 20-
OL,12,Fyear-olds has been increased from
OL,13,F#8.60 to #10 per hour.
OL,15,FBut the Foundation said that bringing
OL,16,Fvarious changes together, the
OL,17,Fdisposable income of a median average
OL,18,Fworking-age household in the UK is
OL,19,Fprojected to fall by #400 in real
OL,20,Fterms, when comparing the financial
OL,21,Fyear of 2025/26 with 2024/25.
