OL,6,FIt said that while many financial
OL,7,Fpressures are beyond the Government's
OL,8,Fcontrol, quickfire measures can help
OL,9,Fto ease the pressure on households'
OL,10,Fbudgets, such as bringing forward
OL,11,Fincreases in the standard allowance of
OL,12,Funiversal credit.
OL,14,FAdam Corlett, principal economist at
OL,15,Fthe Resolution Foundation, said: "The
OL,16,Fnew tax year has arrived, and brings
OL,17,Fwith it higher taxes, even larger bill
OL,18,Fincreases, and benefits that aren't
OL,19,Fkeeping pace with the rising cost of
OL,20,Fliving.
